text: Patrik Prikryl (born 19 September 1992) is a Slovak football defender who currently plays for Dukla Banská Bystrica. ==Club career== ===1. FC Tatran Prešov=== Prikryl made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for Tatran Prešov against Železiarne Podbrezová on 18 February 2018.1.FC TATRAN Prešov - FK Železiarne Podbrezová 18.02.2018, futbalnet.sk ==References== ==External links== * 1.
